{"_path":"/councilor/service/s1010","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"A7生活圈牛角坡橋啟用、變二道路正式通車！","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s1010-1.jpeg","sequence":1010,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/15v2XBsHhV/","author":"牛煦庭","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"牛煦庭"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-06-17T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"a7-生活圈牛角坡橋啟用變二道路正式通車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 生活圈牛角坡橋啟用、變二道路正式通車！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"變一、變二、變三道路，新市鎮基金本來包裹補助 10 億，後因為工程原物料上漲，出現 2 億缺口，我就任立委，積極奔走爭取，內政部國土署也同意補上經費。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如今，變三、變二兩條道路都已完工，剩下的變一道路，由於工法特殊，幾次流標，但經過積極邀標溝通，市府工務局長對於下次招標已有信心，我們不妨拭目以待。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因應變二打通，我們近期也會和客運業者溝通召開協調會，看看公車路線是否配合調整，讓新動線發揮最大效益。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 生活圈逐漸成形，龜山人口迅猛成長，我們會繼續緊盯軟硬體建設進度，讓生活品質改善有感。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1010-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1010-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1010-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1010-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1010-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1010-3.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"a7-生活圈牛角坡橋啟用變二道路正式通車","depth":2,"text":"A7 生活圈牛角坡橋啟用、變二道路正式通車！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s1010.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s1010.md","_extension":"md"}